---
title: Coriander Chicken Thigh Coconut Curry with Spinach and Basmati Rice
description: This Coriander Chicken Thigh Coconut Curry is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
